channel.title: When I try to login to my server, it auto kicks me out?
channel.description:
Hello, when ever I log into my server or anybody else does it auto logs us out. Here is what it says in my runserv [code]Accepted From Local Host Anfrany1 is signing onto server Anfarny1 successfully loaded Anfrany1 signed onto the server Game saved for anfrany1 Client Handler : Client Anfrany1 Disconnected[/code]
Is there anyway to fix this? Thanks!
